{"tid":1210210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊聞重温]青馬大橋上下層行車線、港鐵機場快綫及東涌綫一度封閉","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:24:13.000Z","uid":92615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96c510f55dd51b867f6a4b77507c06739b7eba3f","tid":1210210,"uid":92615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:17:21.000Z","msg":"[2015年]<br />\n青嶼幹線發生通車18年來最嚴重的交通癱瘓事故，一艘躉船昨晚近8時，駛經汲水門大橋時懷疑與大橋碰撞，導致大橋防震警號響起，需要緊急檢查。<br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，青馬大橋上下層行車線、港鐵機場快綫及東涌綫一度封閉。其間青嶼幹線塞滿車輛，交通完全癱瘓達兩小時，不僅市民有家歸不得，來往機場更無路可通，大批旅客被迫要去中環搭船往愉景灣及梅窩，再往機場，場面混亂。"},{"pid":"1f598980d5a24d1784d1e7c2ad3b5131cefc6d82","tid":1210210,"uid":95032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"青馬大橋千奇唔好出事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9def97592f3e20dde80d519f7055ce9ec557528a","tid":1210210,"uid":92615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b700d0f0ca9b78d197cadcaa0d1f894cdfdfc68","tid":1210210,"uid":92615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}